result.name: Association of some single nucleotide polymorphisms with clinical features schizophrenia
result.description: We investigated the associations of DRD3 rs6280, HTR1A rs6295, BDNF rs6265, SCL6A4 rs16965628 and 5HT2A rs7322347 with schizophrenia in a case?control study, and the role of the genotype of several clinical features
result.center: V.P. Serbsky National Medical Research Center for Psychiatry and Narcology
